      "id": 1,
      "text": "Mercerville takes its name from General Hugh Mercer, who died of wounds received at the Battle of Princeton.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        1
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercerville%2C_New_Jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "Washington Crossing Historic Park in Mercerville marks George Washington’s daring December 25, 1776 crossing of the Delaware River.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        9,
